      "acceptanceCriteria": "Correspondence between simulation input parameters and experimental conditions formally documented.",
      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. Input parameter mapping from experimental protocol to simulation boundary conditions documented in the simulation plan. Formal equivalency scoring not required at this model risk level."
